OL,3,CRecord broken for most 34C days in a
OL,4,Cyear as third heatwave hits UK
OL,6,FRecords have tumbled again as Britain
OL,7,Fswelters under its third heatwave of
OL,8,Fthe year, as ITV News' Rachel Younger
OL,9,Fand Ellie Pitt report
OL,11,FWords by ITV News Producer Jennifer
OL,12,FMawby
OL,14,FTemperatures hit 34C on Thursday,
OL,15,Fmeaning this year has seen the most
OL,16,Fdays with 34C or higher in UK history,
OL,17,Fthe Met Office has confirmed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
