OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783653540
OL,3,CRecord broken for most 34C days in a
OL,4,Cyear as third heatwave hits UK
OL,6,FIt comes as new heat alerts have been
OL,7,Fissued as the UK experiences its third
OL,8,Fheatwave in as many months, with
OL,9,Ftemperatures expected to soar as high
OL,10,Fas 36C.
OL,12,FSome schools have cancelled sports
OL,13,Fdays and National Fire Chiefs Council
OL,14,F(NFCC) has warned of wildfires due to
OL,15,Fthe dry weather.
OL,17,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,18,Fupgraded its heat alerts which end at
OL,19,F9pm on Sunday, as the warmth spreads
OL,20,Ffurther north.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
