PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783653540
OL,3,CRecord broken for most 34C days in a
OL,4,Cyear as third heatwave hits UK
OL,6,FAmber alerts are in place for these
OL,7,Fareas of the UK:
OL,9,FThe North East has a yellow heat
OL,10,Falert. Unlike the June heatwave, there
OL,11,Fare currently no red warnings in place.
OL,13,FHigh temperatures increase the risk of
OL,14,Fserious health conditions, including
OL,15,Foverheating and even death, the UKHSA
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
