CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783653540
OL,3,CRecord broken for most 34C days in a
OL,4,Cyear as third heatwave hits UK
OL,6,FProfessor Frankie Swords, NHS national
OL,7,Fmedical director, said ambulance
OL,8,Fservices are "under sustained
OL,9,Fpressure" and that "patients should
OL,10,Falways call 999 in a life-threatening
OL,11,Femergency or 111 if less urgent".
OL,13,FAccording to the NHS, the most
OL,14,Fvulnerable are babies and children
OL,15,Funder five, over 65s and people who
OL,16,Fare pregnant or have long-term health
OL,17,Fconditions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
