PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783653540
OL,3,CRecord broken for most 34C days in a
OL,4,Cyear as third heatwave hits UK
OL,6,FThey advise people to stay in the
OL,7,Fshade, drink plenty of water and look
OL,8,Fout for vulnerable members of the
OL,9,Fcommunity.
OL,11,FThe Department of Education said
OL,12,Fschools are expected to remain fully
OL,13,Fopen, but may relax uniform rules so
OL,14,Fchildren can wear looser clothing.
OL,16,FSouth East England officially met
OL,17,Fheatwave criteria on Monday evening
OL,18,Fafter temperatures were higher than
OL,19,F28C for three days.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
