FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783653540
OL,3,CRecord broken for most 34C days in a
OL,4,Cyear as third heatwave hits UK
OL,6,FThe warm weather will continue next
OL,7,Fweek with some chance of thundery
OL,8,Fshowers.
OL,10,FTom Crabtree, Deputy Chief Forecaster
OL,11,Fat the Met Office said: "While
OL,12,Ftemperatures are expected to ease
OL,13,Facross southeast England through the
OL,14,Fweekend and into next week, it won't
OL,15,Fbe a straightforward end to the warm
OL,16,Fweather."
